    "desc": "Bizfluent equips entrepreneurs with the tools and tactics they need to build and grow their small businesses. Whether they are just starting their first business or they are repeat entrepreneurs refreshing their knowledge base, Bizfluent provides the information they need to successfully establish and run their ventures.",
    "navbar": "",
    "text": "SKIP TO CONTENT\nSKIP TO SITE INDEX\n►\nSTART Your Business\nFINANCE Your Business\nMANAGE Your Business\nGet fluent in minding your business\nlatest\nGrants for Nonprofit Youth Sports\nWhat Does an Employer Pay for Unemployment?\nAre Nine-Digit ZIP Codes Required in the USA?\nHow to Get a Material Donation From Lowe's\nstart your business\nBusiness Ideas\nBusiness Plan\nLegal\nPermits/licenses\nMarket Research\nOffice Supplies\nbusiness plan\nHow to Develop a Business Strategy\nbusiness ideas\nHow to Create a Benefits Statement\nmarket research\nDefinition of Consumer Market\nbusiness plan\nHow to Start a Ceramics Business\nbusiness ideas\nHow to Open a Cosmetics Boutique\nmarket research\nHow to Write Brand Copy\nbusiness plan\nHow to Lay Out a Fresh Produce Department\nbusiness ideas\nHow to Make Money Making Personalized Items\nbusiness plan\nHow to Write a Website Report\nlegal\nThe Organizational Structure of Labor Unions\nmanagement\nEffective Virtual Communication\ntaxes\nHow to Obtain a Confirmation Letter for an Assigned EIN Number\nbusiness operations\nHow Do I Mute My Phone During a Conference Call\nlegal\nHow to Find an Employer Registration Number\nfinance your business\nFunding/financing\nAccounting\nTaxes\nSalary/payroll\naccounting\nHow Does the Economy Work?\naccounting\nHow to Calculate Cost Escalation\naccounting\nHow to Calculate Revenue Per Employee\nsalary payroll\nHow to Calculate Applied Overhead Costs\naccounting\nHow to Calculate Carrying Costs\naccounting\nHow to Journalize Cash Withdrawals for Personal Use\naccounting\nManual vs. Computerized Accounting Systems\naccounting\nHow to Audit Bank Accounts\naccounting\nHow to Calculate Seating Capacity of a Restaurant\nfunding financing\nHow To Account for a Donated Asset\nbusiness operations\nHow to Supervise Staff in Remote Locations\nbusiness ideas\nWhat Is a Home-Based Business?\nlegal\nHow Does Unemployment Insurance Work? A Guide for Employers\nsalary payroll\nManaging Payroll & Employees During the COVID-19 Crisis\nWhether you are starting your first company or you are a dedicated entrepreneur diving into a new venture, Bizfluent is here to equip you with the tactics, tools and information to establish and run your ventures.\nBizfluent\nAbout\nContact\nCareers\nAdvertise\nLegal\nTerms of Use\nPrivacy Policy\nCopyright Policy\nAccessbility\nDo Not Sell My Personal Information\n© 2023 Leaf Group Ltd. / Leaf Group Media, All Rights Reserved.",
